時真係會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋作為絲打既我都知有時就算有冇另一半都可以會有唔開心<br />\n我留我tg俾你呀 等你覺得真係想可以有多個人去傾 <a href=\"https://t.me/comeaddme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcomeaddme&d=WR3KeWjj0JuqOJLXqtgwADA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f426769b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/comeaddme</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15599cca05f1d3f40e7e494e1f50417da0567a91","tid":974262,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"加油"}]}